nnections are, in\ngeneral, only proper subsets satisfying the properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Jan 2018 16:24:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Feb 2018 15:24:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 28 Jan 2019 16:41:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-29"}
